* 7-Segment Display (common cathode)
* Pins: a b c d e f g
* Each segment is an LED with 330-ohm series resistor to GND.

.model led_diode D(Is=1e-14 N=1.5 BV=5 IBV=1e-3)

.subckt 7seg_display a b c d e f g
Ra a seg_a_int 330
Da seg_a_int 0 led_diode
Rb b seg_b_int 330
Db seg_b_int 0 led_diode
Rc c seg_c_int 330
Dc seg_c_int 0 led_diode
Rd d seg_d_int 330
Dd seg_d_int 0 led_diode
Re e seg_e_int 330
De seg_e_int 0 led_diode
Rf f seg_f_int 330
Df seg_f_int 0 led_diode
Rg g seg_g_int 330
Dg seg_g_int 0 led_diode
.ends 7seg_display
